        "title": "Indian used cars dataset",
        "subtitle": "Vehicle listing from August 2025",
        "description": "This dataset comprises a collection of used car listings from Spinny, a prominent Indian car-reseller. It offers valuable information for various analytical tasks, particularly for predicting the resale value of a car. The dataset contains details about 8104 cars with 14 features ranging from car model to number of previous owners.\n\nKey features of this dataset include:\n\nVehicle Details: Make, model, and variant, which are crucial for assessing a car's market value.\n\nCar Specifications: Features such as the number of previous owners, body type, transmission type, and registration year, all of which significantly influence resale value.\n\nGeographical Data: The dataset can be used to analyze how resale values vary across different Indian states. For example, it could be used to investigate why certain regions, like Delhi, might have a lower resale value for used cars.\n\nMarket Insights: This dataset also provides a basis for understanding car-buyer preferences in the Indian market, such as popular models, body types, and transmission choices.\n\n=== About this file ===\n\nAbout this file\nThe file contains details about 8104 used cars. Each car has 14 features associated with it.\n\n\n=== Columns & descriptions ===\n\ncity: City in which the car is being sold\nmake: Manufacturer of the car\nmodel: Model name of the car\nvariant: Specific variant of the car\nmileage: Number of kilometers driven\nmake_year: Manufacturing year of the car\nprice: List price of the car\nfuel_type: fuel type: petrol/diesel/CNG\nno_of_owners: Number of previous owners of the car\ncolor: Exterior color of the car\nbody_type: [no description]\ntransmission: [no description]\nregistration_year: [no description]\nlatest_publish_date: [no description]\n",
